  "prompt": "How do you see a deleted comment on instagram?",
  "response": "If a comment is deleted on Instagram, it is removed from the platform and cannot be viewed by users. Instagram does not provide a feature to view deleted comments. Once a comment is deleted, it's gone for good, unless the person who posted it or Instagram itself has a backup or record of it, which is not accessible to the general public.\n\nIf you're trying to keep a record of comments, you might consider taking screenshots or using third-party services that offer such functionalities, but be aware that using third-party apps can pose privacy and security risks, and may violate Instagram's terms of service. Always prioritize your account's security and privacy.",
